{
  "chapter": "第二章：椭圆定义与数学严谨性探究",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "id": "ch02_s05_intro",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "thinking" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "是不是只要「和等于常数」，就一定能画出椭圆？我们来做一次严谨性检验。" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "image", "src": "/labimage/ch02/sum_conditions.svg" },
      "next": "ch02_s05_triangle"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch02_s05_triangle",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "normal" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "正常情况下，M、F\u2081、F\u2082 构成三角形，两边之和大于第三边。这时候，我们能得到一个圆润的椭圆。" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "image", "src": "/labimage/ch02/sum_conditions.svg" },
      "next": "ch02_s05_degenerate"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch02_s05_degenerate",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "thinking" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "如果常数（绳长）恰好等于两点间距呢？我们知道三角形两边之和大于第三边，但此时要求距离和等于第三边，所以这个时候构不成三角形。这时候，轨迹只是一条线段。" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "image", "src": "/labimage/ch02/sum_conditions.svg" },
      "next": "ch02_s05_impossible"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch02_s05_impossible",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "surprised" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "如果常数比两点间距还要小，那连三角形的基本原则都违背了。此时，轨迹不存在。" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "image", "src": "/labimage/ch02/sum_conditions.svg" },
      "next": "ch02_s06_definition"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch02_s06_definition",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "happy", "action": "excited" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "至此，我们终于得到了椭圆最完美的定义：我们把平面内与两定点 F\u2081、F\u2082 的距离的和等于常数，且这个常数大于线段 F\u2081F\u2082 的长的点的轨迹叫做椭圆。" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "image", "src": "/labimage/ch02/ellipse_definition.svg" },
      "next": "ch02_s06_video_intro"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch02_s06_video_intro",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "excited" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "来吧，欣赏一段由数学公式生成的艺术——让我们看看这个定义是如何幻化成美妙曲线的。" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "image", "src": "/labimage/ch02/ellipse_definition.svg" },
      "next": "ch02_s06_video"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch02_s06_video",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "happy" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "看，点 M 优雅地划过，始终满足到两个定点的距离之和为常数，且这个常数大于线段 F\u2081F\u2082 的长度，一条完美的椭圆就此诞生。" },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "video",
        "src": "/labvideo/ch02/ellipse_manim.mp4",
        "autoplay": true,
        "loop": true
      },
      "next": "ch02_s07_foci"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch02_s07_foci",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "normal" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "记住这两个名字。F\u2081 和 F\u2082 叫做焦点，|F\u2081F\u2082| 叫做焦距。焦距是两定点间的距离，长轴是椭圆上两点的最短距离，短轴是椭圆上最近两点的距离。焦点和焦距，是椭圆的「灵魂坐标」。" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "image", "src": "/labimage/ch02/foci_focal_distance.svg" },
      "next": "ch02_s07_preview"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch02_s07_preview",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "thinking" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "现在，概念提炼完成了。下一节，我们将拿起笛卡尔的画笔，把这个几何定义，翻译成数学方程！" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "image", "src": "/labimage/ch02/foci_focal_distance.svg" },
      "next": "ch02_s07_end"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch02_s07_end",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": { "expression": "happy", "action": "bounce" },
      "dialogue": { "text": "准备好了吗？下一章见！" },
      "blackboard": { "type": "image", "src": "/labimage/ch02/foci_focal_distance.svg" },
      "next": null
    }
  ]
}
